text: Captain Kidd is a 1945 American adventure movie directed by Rowland V. Lee and starring Charles Laughton, Randolph Scott, Barbara Britton, John Carradine, Gilbert Roland, John Qualen, Sheldon Leonard, William Farnum, Henry Daniell, Reginald Owen. It was distributed by United Artists and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1946. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1945 movies Category:1940s adventure movies Category:1940s American adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Rowland V. Lee
